<plot>Zorg (Mark Wijsman), an 8 year old boy, is a very sensitive and intelligent boy. One day, his father, who is a hard-working, stressful man, suffers from a heart attack just after he had a phone call with his boss, Boshart. The father is brought to a hospital and meanwhile Zorg invites the boss to his home for dinner and prepares, together with his 80-year old neighbor, who seems to have magic powers, a meal with rats, maggots and other dirty things.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?131139</url></doc>
